British aid worker David Haines has been executed by ISIS militants, according to a video posted on a website associated with the group on Saturday, making him the third Western captive to be killed by the Islamist extremist group in recent weeks. The ISIS video post showing Haines’ beheading called his execution “a message to the allies of America.”

